EXPAND(1)                        User Commands
EXPAND(1)



NNAAMMEE
       expand - convert tabs to spaces

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
       eexxppaanndd
       [_O_P_T_I_O_N]... [_F_I_L_E]...

DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       Convert  tabs in each FILE to spaces, writing to
       standard output.  With no FILE, or when FILE is -,
       read standard input.

       Mandatory arguments to long options are  mandatory
       for  short  options too.

       --ii, ----iinniittiiaall
              do not convert tabs after non blanks

       --tt, ----ttaabbss=_N_U_M_B_E_R
              have tabs NUMBER characters apart, not 8

       --tt, ----ttaabbss=_L_I_S_T
              use comma separated list of explicit tab
              positions

       ----hheellpp display this help and exit

       ----vveerrssiioonn
              output version information and exit

AAUUTTHHOORR
       Written by David MacKenzie.

RREEPPOORRTTIINNGG BBUUGGSS
