SSEEEE AALLSSOO
       unexpand(1)

       The full documentation for eexxppaanndd
       is maintained as  a  Texinfo  manual.  If  the
       iinnffoo  and eexxppaanndd programs are
       properly installed at your site, the command

              iinnffoo eexxppaanndd

       should give you access to the complete manual.



expand 6.7                       December 2006
